    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基于物理的高尔夫</h2>在司机、木杆、铁杆和推杆之间切换，每种杆提供不同的方式来攻克球场。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/5c4cfbf652c5d1671e610067f956613e.poster.avif?t=1721670291\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/5c4cfbf652c5d1671e610067f956613e.webm?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/5c4cfbf652c5d1671e610067f956613e.mp4?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >平台游戏</h2>高尔夫只是开始。跳跃、冲刺并通过棘手的平台部分导航。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/55849b483ea4c1d3da8dbc6dbbca28b9.poster.avif?t=1721670291\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/55849b483ea4c1d3da8dbc6dbbca28b9.webm?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/55849b483ea4c1d3da8dbc6dbbca28b9.mp4?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人游戏</h2>与最多12个朋友在线玩。或者，如果你感觉冒险，可以加入公共大厅，认识新的高尔夫朋友！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/623f609f14e4cba2043d54f94888f949.poster.avif?t=1721670291\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/623f609f14e4cba2043d54f94888f949.webm?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/623f609f14e4cba2043d54f94888f949.mp4?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关卡编辑器</h2>使用内置的关卡编辑器释放你的创造力。设计自定义关卡，并通过Steam Workshop与社区分享。玩和评价社区创建的地图，享受无尽的高尔夫冒险！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/a90ce407f8b27da1a4a00822666f90f8.poster.avif?t=1721670291\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/a90ce407f8b27da1a4a00822666f90f8.webm?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263920/extras/a90ce407f8b27da1a4a00822666f90f8.mp4?t=1721670291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >给我们反馈！</h2>",
